# Task cards (Mandatory)

Full contract: [Task-Card-Standard.md](../../docs/02_FLUTTER_MIGRATION/Task-Card-Standard.md)

## When editing Rewards / Arena task lists (`VitTaskCard`, mission sections)

1. **Use `VitTaskCard`** — no page-local `_TaskCard` with fixed `minHeight`.
2. **Intrinsic height** — do not set `VitCard.height` or `constraints.minHeight` on task rows; no `buttonHero + x7 + x5`.
3. **Tokens** — `taskCardPadding`, `taskCardProgressHeight`, `taskCardListGap`, and related `taskCard*` spacing.
4. **Status pills** — map domain status to `VitTaskCardStatus`; do not duplicate pill labels on pages.

## Verify before batch complete

```bash
cd flutter_app
flutter test test/shared/widgets/vit_shared_widgets_test.dart --name "VitTaskCard"
flutter test test/quality/task_card_guardrail_test.dart --reporter=compact
```
